OL,5, Just before she left for school on the 
OL,6, afternoon of 16 September last year,   
OL,7, nine year-old Zin Nwe Phyo was thrilled
OL,8, to be given a new pair of sandals by   
OL,9, her uncle.                             
OL,11,FShe made him a cup of coffee, put on   
OL,12,Fthe shoes and headed off to school, a  
OL,13,F10-minute walk away in the village of  
OL,14,FLet Yet Kone in central Myanmar.       
OL,15,FShortly afterwards, her uncle recalls, 
OL,16,Fhe saw two helicopters circling over   
OL,17,Fthe village. Suddenly they started     
OL,18,Fshooting.                              
